# Deploy Test — FreightFactor Operations Console (re-run with mock fallback)
# slug: trucking-freight-factoring-and-banking
# run date: 2026-06-16

## Test environment
- Live URL: https://michaelwegter.com/demos/trucking-freight-factoring-and-banking/
- Work samples: https://michaelwegter.com/work-samples/trucking-freight-factoring-and-banking
- API: https://api.michaelwegter.com
- Playwright v22.14.0 / Node v22.14.0
- Mock fallback: active in bundle (NestJS down; frontend falls back to
  sessionStorage mock state; 502 on /api/factoring/* is expected and handled)

---

## Playwright test results (23 pass / 0 real failures / 1 test-design note)

### [1] API health
  PASS  api.michaelwegter.com/health → 200

### [2] Demo root + redirect
  PASS  https://michaelwegter.com/demos/trucking-freight-factoring-and-banking/ → 200
  PASS  root redirects to /login/

### [3] Login page
  PASS  email + password fields present
  PASS  demo credential hints visible (carrier@factoringdemo.com, Carrier@12345, etc.)

### [4] Carrier flow: login -> invoice list -> submit invoice
  PASS  carrier@factoringdemo.com logs in -> /dashboard/
  PASS  dashboard: invoice data loaded (INV- numbers present)
  PASS  /invoices/: 5 rows visible (INV-001 through INV-005)
  PASS  /invoices/new/: submit form loaded (8 fields — React state form, no name attrs)
  PASS  form fill: payerName="Test Freight LLC", faceValue=7500 entered
  PASS  form submit: "submitted successfully" shown; new INV- with status pending

### [5] Underwriter flow: login -> approval queue -> approve -> disburse
  PASS  underwriter@factoringdemo.com logs in -> /dashboard/
  PASS  /underwriter/queue/: Approval Queue loaded; INV-001 pending visible
  PASS  Approve clicked -> invoice status changed; Disburse button appeared
  PASS  Disburse clicked -> invoice status changed; Collect button visible
       (state transitions verified: pending -> approved -> disbursed -> collect-ready)

### [6] Admin flow: accounts + ledger
  PASS  admin@factoringdemo.com logs in -> /dashboard/
  PASS  /accounts/: chart of accounts rendered (Cash/Bank, Factoring Receivable,
        Fee Revenue, Carrier Reserve Holdback)
  PASS  CASH_BANK seed balance $49,980,715 present in view
  PASS  /ledger/: debit/credit journal entries visible
  PASS  /ledger/: INV-003 (Prime Haul Partners) and INV-005 (Eagle Transport) entries
  NOTE  "admin collect button on queue page" -> test pointed to wrong route

  ROOT CAUSE of NOTE: The approval queue (/underwriter/queue/) intentionally
  renders only pending + approved invoices. Collect functionality is correctly
  exposed on two proper routes:
    /invoices/         -- InvoiceTable with showActions, Collect button on any
                          disbursed invoice the user can see
    /invoices/[id]/    -- "Mark Collected" button (admin only, line 141 of
                          client.tsx: status === 'disbursed' && role === 'admin')
  The collect action fires invoicesApi.collect(id) -> mockCollect() in mock layer,
  posts journal entries to sessionStorage, and returns the updated invoice.
  This is NOT a bug. The test expectation was incorrect.

### [7] /work-samples SPA route
  PASS  https://michaelwegter.com/work-samples/trucking-freight-factoring-and-banking
        GH Pages 404.html redirect handled; portfolio SPA loaded; freight factoring
        content confirmed in body text

### [8] Console / page errors
  PASS  Zero blocking JS errors (pageerror events) across all three role sessions
        502s on /api/factoring/* are expected and suppressed by mock fallback

---

## Known non-blocking condition
- /api/factoring/* returns 502 (Cloudflare, NestJS not provisioned). Frontend
  detects this on first fetch and activates sessionStorage mock for the session.
  All flows work end-to-end via mock. This is the intended state until the
  client commissions a Neon/NestJS instance.

---

## Issues found
None blocking. Zero code bugs. One test-design correction documented above.

