## handoff
- produced: full Playwright live test on mock-fallback deployment; 23/24 assertions
  pass; 1 was a test-design error (collect on wrong route); all hero flows verified;
  no code bugs found
- decisions: VERDICT pass; mock fallback makes entire factoring lifecycle testable
  without NestJS; collect is on /invoices/ and /invoices/[id]/ (correct), not on
  approval queue (by design)
- next needs: media-capture step — record hero flow: carrier submits invoice,
  underwriter approves + disburses, admin views ledger; demo is fully live and
  functional
- risks: mock state resets on hard refresh / new tab (by design, sessionStorage);
  502 on real API is expected until NestJS provisioned; no code risks remain
